folder: Sidney Place & State Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)

Sidney Place, North from State Street. In the background is seen the steeple of St. Charles Borromeo R.C. Church.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, further north on Sidney Place.
February 22, 1930.
F.L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, showing the same view at a later date.
June 1, 1934.

F.L. Sperr.
